&lt;li&gt;Identify, develop, and execute high-impact partnership opportunities that drive new logo acquisition and long-term revenue growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage an established network to generate qualified pipeline and accelerate market entry across key European jurisdictions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a trusted advisor to prospects and partners on evolving regulatory requirements, including CARF, DAC8, and broader global information reporting frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
