&lt;li&gt;Represent Taxbit at industry events, conferences, and executive forums to strengthen brand presence and build executive-level relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide market feedback and insights to inform product roadmap, positioning, and regional strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development of scalable partnership programs across EMEA in collaboration with global leadership&lt;/li&gt;
