&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of identifying opportunities to build, test, and scale AI-powered solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sees AI as a force multiplier and actively looks for ways to enhance team performance through innovation &amp;amp; curiosity.&lt;/li&gt;
